</listitem><listitem><para>At 100% power, the ratio is equal to 1. <simplesect kind="return"><para>The duty cycle applied on the hardware, or 0 if the dimmer is offline The firing ratio represents the actual proportion of time the dimmer is conducting power to the load within each AC cycle. It is computed based on the remapped duty cycle and eventually the power LUT if enabled. </para>
